'''Tisyn-C''' was a highly potent [[Nerve toxin/Legends|nerve agent]] that caused convulsions and dementia followed by paralytic respiratory failure and, eventually, [[Death/Legends|death]]. [[Graylite]], a type of [[Armor/Legends|armor]] used by the [[Balawai militia]] on [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]], was rated against [[Gas/Legends|gas]] exposure, though the rating did not extend to Tisyn-C.<ref name="SP">[[Shatterpoint (novel)|''Shatterpoint'']]</ref>
